      "kind": "partial_refused",
      "expected": "If partial publication is disallowed, the control plane withholds completion until accounting is fully resolved."
    },
    {
      "kind": "partial_allowed",
      "expected": "If partial publication is allowed, the control plane may emit a partial summary while unresolved identities remain."
